'''Herbert Harrison "Bert" Tilsley''' was played by [[Peter Dudley]]. He was the first husband of [[Ivy Brennan]] and the father of [[Brian Tilsley]]. Bert died in January 1984 of a heart attack while in hospital, following a nervous breakdown. Actor Peter Dudley had died three months earlier from the same condition.
